TEXT.S: = An-ta-man-subal = ayda idaw ku sepatay nu binacadan, Taan-taman-zen "Strait Island", Ciwluo-wa-zen, Wunci-zen atu Santi-neie-zen. Anta-man subalan a mapuletay nu lumeniay a tademaw caay tu pikihatiya tu kitakid, kaisa atu i hekalay atademaw masasuadih. picidekan tu Santi-neie-zen mikitalakaw tu duma a kitidaan nu tademaw, palecad tu talakaw han makaala tu caynem-sep - caynem-lim kunhu ku talakaw, caay kaw apulet ku sausi tu nuhenian " mapuletay han a caylim-sep kunhun", nipisausi ayda nu maudipay cacay tu a malebut ku maudipay. Ciwluo-wa a binacadan tulim-sep - sipsep-sep ku tademaw. 4:Strait Island160-1651501000250-400
